training. ; Photo, (San Diego Edition) Some cliff divers display classic form, 
but others just want a thrill, not style points. ; Photo, (San Diego Edition) 
The one must for a successful cliff dive? Plenty of water. DAVID McNEW / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
