<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Pacific Scientific Co.: The Newport Beach-based manufacturer of industrial and 
aerospace products posted second-quarter earnings of $1.8 million, up from 
$859,000 in the year-earlier quarter. 
</P>
<P>
Revenue rose 12% to $46.9 million from $41.9 million. For the six months, 
earnings totaled $2.7 million, up from $1.7 million a year earlier. Revenue 
increased 9%, to $91.7 million from $84.3 million. 
</P>
</TEXT>
