<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Technology Marketing Inc.: The Irvine-based computer-products company lost 
$98,177 for its fiscal 1991 first quarter, in contrast with earnings of 
$245,658 for the comparable quarter last year. Revenue for the quarter ended 
May 31 declined 35%, to $1.7 million from $2.6 million. 
</P>
