</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
NIBBLES AND BITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Kenneth Williams 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"Lounge Lizzards," the late-night parody show that opened July 6 at Saddleback 
College's Cabaret Theatre, has closed early because of poor ticket sales. It 
originally was scheduled to run through Aug. 11. Information: (714) 582-4656. 
</P>
</TEXT>
