</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
SPORTS FRANCHISES; BASEBALL; TEAM OWNERS; SENIOR PROFESSIONAL BASEBALL 
ASSOCIATION; PHOENIX (AZ) -- ATHLETICS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA072590-0117 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 252232 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 25, 1990, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 2; Column 6; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
27 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The NFL said it would discontinue developmental squads, the six-player units of 
rookies who were allowed to practice with the regular 47-man teams last year. 
</P>
